        <updateDate>2014-04-29T21:56:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Appropriate Care for Disabled Veterans Act - Repeals the termination date of (thus, reinstates) the requirement for an annual report from the Secretary of Veterans Affairs (VA) on the Secretary's compliance, by facility and by service-network, with requirements for managing the provision of hospital care and medical services furnished to veterans with service-connected disabilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
